prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 Low is the latest silhouette to honor the annual French basketball tournament, Quai 54.

The Air Jordan 1 Low Quai 54 (2021) is designed after fabric patterns originating in West Africa. The upper is constructed of black nubuck and white leather. Greyscale patterned fabric makes up the heel of the shoe, while a white Jumpman logo and red �54� are boldly embroidered on the tongue. Lastly, a semi-translucent red outsole adds additional detail to the Jordan 1 low silhouette.

The Air Jordan 1 Low Quai 54 (2021) released in July of 2021 for $120.
